led church represents the sense of history one feels on the Savannah River Scenic Byway. Location: South Carolina (33.850° N 82.260° W) Status: Public domain.","credit":"Public domain","pageUrl":"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Savannah_River_Scenic_Byway_-_A_Charming_Old_Church_-_NARA_-_7721668.jpg"},{"url":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/8/8a/Savannah_River_Scenic_Byway_-_Birdhouse_Exhibit_at_the_Thurmond_Reservoir_Visitor_Center_-_NARA_-_7721649.jpg","full":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/8/8a/Savannah_River_Scenic_Byway_-_Birdhouse_Exhibit_at_the_Thurmond_Reservoir_Visitor_Center_-_NARA_-_7721649.jpg","cap":"Birdhouse Exhibit at the Thurmond Reservoir Visitor Center","desc":"Press the buttons on these birdhouses to hear what each bird you'll find near the reservoir sounds like. Location: South Carolina (33.651° N 82.125° W) Status: Public domain. Photo by K. Armstrong","credit":"K. Armstrong, U.S. Department of Transportation · Public domain","pageUrl":"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Savannah_River_Scenic_Byway_-_Birdhouse_Exhibit_at_the_Thurmond_Reservoir_Visitor_Center_-_NARA_-_7721649.jpg"},{"url":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/e/e2/Savannah_River_Scenic_Byway_-_Calhoun_Falls_State_Recreation_Area_-_NARA_-_7721634.jpg","full":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/e/e2/Savannah_River_Scenic_Byway_-_Calhoun_Falls_State_Recreation_Area_-_NARA_-_7721634.jpg","cap":"Calhoun Falls State Recreation Area","desc":"Calhoun Falls offers some of the best fishing spots in the state, along with a seasonal tennis court, camping, hiking trails, and a swimming area. Location: South Carolina (34.109° N 82.613° W) Status: Public domain. Photo by K. Armstrong","credit":"Public domain","pageUrl":"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Savannah_River_Scenic_Byway_-_Calhoun_Falls_State_Recreation_Area_-_NARA_-_7721634.jpg"},{"url":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/5/5f/Savannah_River_Scenic_B